### Supply a locally-issued HS256 JWT with sub=customer-1 and scope="orders:read orders:write".
@token = replace-me
@orderId = replace-after-create

POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: tutorial-order-001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {"sku": "JAVA-25", "quantity": 2, "unitPrice": 19.95, "currency": "EUR"}
  ]
}

### Repeating the exact request/key returns the original order; changing the body is 409.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders?status=PENDING&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{{orderId}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### A second confirm is 409 application/problem+json.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{{orderId}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
